[The location of the outbreak can be seen on the map included in the
OIE report at the source URL above.

This appears to be a much delayed report on a 28 Jul 2010 outbreak in
the village of Okruhle, but in the same general area of Svidnik as the
2 previous outbreaks in this part of Slovakia, which were in Sobos on
9 Jul 2010 (see ProMED-mail Anthrax, bovine - Slovakia: (PV) OIE
20100713.2346) and in Stefurov on 16 Jul 2010. - Mod.MHJ]
